description._content: Original Collection: Withycombe Family Collection Image Description: James Withycombe home in Corvallis, Oregon. The Withycombe House was donated to Oregon Agricultural College and later used as a Home Management House. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
